I am in semi-desperate need of a photo of [Max Miedinger](http://web.archive.org/web/20131023173233/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Max%20Miedinger) for a piece I am putting together about the design of [Helvetica](http://web.archive.org/web/20131023173233/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Helvetica). I can't seem to find any photos anywhere of the man. Does anyone have a photo or a scan they can send/post? I would be eternally grateful!

Andrea

